Program: Discovery
Title: Anthropology - the angry anthropologist
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jry1p
Last Broadcast Date: 13 March 2002
First in a series examining the discipline of social anthropology. First in a series examining how the discipline of social anthropology has evolved from the pursuit of the exotic to the mundane. This edition appraises the life and work of controversial British anthropologist Colin Turnbull. Presenter: Anna Buckley. Show less